data.description:
Your new home awaits! This two-story gem features 3 beds, 2.5 baths, and a double garage on a generous over half an acre lot. Enjoy cozy moments in the living room with a fireplace; perfect for making memories. The charming kitchen, complete with an eat-in area is the perfect place to cook your favorite meals or simply order take out. The backyard is a dream with a beautiful deck overlooking the fenced backyard. Your search is over – welcome home!
